I am super excited to announce my newest illustration theme for International Women’s History Month! —————————————
My inspiration and concept comes from road signs, because they are made to draw your attention to something important. These designs are to celebrate the women in your past, present, and future!
—————————————
My designs will be up for sale as merch on my Redbubble as soon as I post them and I would LOVE for you to enjoy them as a gift to yourself or for someone else!

summary: I painted this for my mom as a Christmas present. It's me holding our little chubby dog Yoda when I was 11. We all miss him so...
caption: I painted this for my mom as a Christmas present. It’s me holding our little chubby dog Yoda when I was 11. We all miss him so much. It may seem dumb to people who see dogs as just pets but he was my brother (and a better one than my human bother), my mother’s son, and a father figure to the whole pack. We love you wherever you are my little dude.
